                     <interp inst="t18191201-7-verdict51" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               Of stealing to the value of 39 s. only
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18191201-7-punish52" type="punishmentDescription">
